      "options": {"content": "# Data Platform Demo - Monitoring Dashboard\n\n## How to see more data\n\n1. Go to **Airflow** (localhost:8080) and trigger `demo_pipeline` multiple times\n2. StatsD metrics will accumulate in Prometheus\n3. The charts above will populate with DAG success rates, task durations, etc.\n\n## Current Status\n\n- **Kafka**: Running (data-kafka:9092)\n- **Airflow**: Running (airflow/airflow)\n- **PostgreSQL**: Running with 9838 events, 3 dbt models\n- **Grafana**: You are here!\n\n## Data Pipeline Stats\n- 9838 user events across 3 days\n- 500 unique users\n- 4 dbt models built (dim_users, dim_products, fct_user_events_daily)\n- 15/15 data quality tests passing\n", "mode": "markdown"},
